<div class="thumbinner" style="width:242px;"><a href="/wiki/File:SnowflakesWilsonBentley.jpg" class="image" title="Snowflake photos by Wilson Bentley circa 1902"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c2/SnowflakesWilsonBentley.jpg/240px-SnowflakesWilsonBentley.jpg" width="240" height="307" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:SnowflakesWilsonBentley.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Snowflake photos by Wilson Bentley circa 1902</div>
